Find My Location Free is a completely free simple but useful Android app I designed to get the latitude and longitude of a location and to display it on screen and on a map.  The app can also take a favorite location and save it for later use.  Users are also given an option to navigate to a previously saved location using Google Maps Navigation. This tagging and navigation to favorite locations can be helpful if you park in a large parking lot, for example, and you don't know where you left your car.

For more information the app is available for <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.latitudeandlongitude.location&amp;hl=en">free</a> on the Google Play Store.  The open source GitHub repo is available <a href="https://github.com/bmisljen/locationapp">here</a>.

