}

.sidebar-nav li a:active,
.sidebar-nav li a:focus {
    text-decoration: none;
}
[/code]

The "sidebar-nav -&gt; sidebar-brand" section contains styling information for each section in the menu such as the "About" section:

[code language="css"]
.sidebar-nav &gt; .sidebar-brand {
